## Introduction

This repository contains original creative works developed for the **Mimesis Public Safety Project**, an original fictional public safety identity system created for the Mimesis Roleplay universe.

For the purposes of this license, **Project Assets** include, but are not limited to:

- Logos
- Badges
- Seals
- Department branding
- Vehicle liveries
- Graphics
- Design standards
- Documentation
- Templates
- Source artwork
- Production exports
- Typography
- Uniform designs
- Any other original materials contained within this repository

By accessing, cloning, downloading, viewing, or contributing to this repository, you acknowledge and agree to the terms of this license.

